snippet.title: Basements & Bugbears Trailer
snippet.description:
Hey there. You probably found this video from the game's page anyway, you sneaky nerd.

On the off chance you didn't, you can download it here: https://neonblade.itch.io/bandb

We won't make you, you can just enjoy the trailer.

It's basically 1/100th of a best-hits let's play.

but without commentary and the game is played by a robot I forced to play it as a slave so I could get footage

...

okay so maybe it's not like a let's play at all
